author: ehillenius
msg: extracted interface for intercepting request targets on RequestCycle#setRequestTarget

author: jcompagner
msg: Page warns if it wants to be stateless but isn't because of some components.
By default Forms and Links are not stateless but those 2 are.
Now when a page is bookmarkable and a component says it wants to or can be stateless
then a bookmarkable interface request is generated (always) but with the pageid
also added to the interface request.
After it gets back it tries to resolve the page from the session. If possible it uses that
if not it creates the page.

author: frankbille
msg: WicketTester.clickLink now supports AjaxFallbackLinks. clickLink now takes a boolean parameter which can be used to test what happens in non-ajax situations. A helper method which is the same as the old clickLink is created for default testing of AJAX links.
